<plot>Friendly, brave, outgoing, yet shy of the opposite sex, Chander Kapoor (Bobby Deol), lives an exciting life. To add to this excitement, he helps his friend, Jay, elope with Neena, the daughter of a suspended and rogue police inspector (Mukesh Rishi). Neena's friend, Pooja (Karisma Kapoor) has a crush on Chander, and phones him on the sly, teasing him. When Chander finds out it is Pooja, he too falls in love with her. Pooja family life is stressful, an alcoholic dad (Anjan Shrivastav), and a spiteful mom (Smita Jaykar). Pooja decides from run away from this atmosphere, and ends up abducted in a brothel. Neena's dad wants to avenge his humiliation, and will go to any lenght, even kill Chander. With Chander on the defensive with Neena's dad, what will be the outcome of Pooja?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?020689</url></doc>
